{"tid":262123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港對續暫被支那化香港人可以點？","createTime":"2017-05-29T03:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T05:19:03.000Z","uid":10672,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3131c17753e11ffbc5c3be3c04d8e59b87cbf8fb","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"反抗都冇用"},{"pid":"fad1717c0ec511082fc8f8c3cf89d2239b6987bc","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"大量支那小朋友同支那人黎香港讀書同住<br />\n18:30播支那歌<br />\n<br />\n香港政府根本唔係幫香港人<br />\n<br />\n政治究竟係乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n香港人一日做唔到終極團結<br />\n始終有一日就會支化<br />\n<br />\n黃雨傘都未去到終極團結<br />\n<br />\n如果連警犬都一齊團結<br />\n<br />\n要反支化<br />\n大量支那小朋友同支那人黎香港讀書同住<br />\n18:30播支那歌<br />\n<br />\n其實要取消上述2項 香港人先有得救<br />\n<br />\n斷估 香港人做唔到可以影響到支那國<br />\n<br />\n而家香港政府 都唔係為香港切想<br />\n香港政府一早支化左<br />\n<br />\n根本 香港玩完。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7bc65a6ebdd12d926b7148209b32df9095750639","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"再負皮就一定係支那狗<br />\n如果唔係 導出你的論點吧"},{"pid":"bb1cc64d601e9d2b30368f151ceeb25f679666d8","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1413f29b575361790f94241d9a6333db8c82746","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:04:32.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/254731/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/254731/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"339c7aefca4f27b4bdd5488f561375bcd2dacfc9","tid":262123,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:08:18.000Z","msg":"標題打錯字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"